Summary: NOTE: planner-create-task-from-buffer in a calendar buffer will use the currently-selected date for the task
Keywords: feature

	* planner.el (planner-create-task-from-buffer): Default date to
	date currently selected in calendar. Do not prompt if creating
	task based on that date. Thanks to Yvonne Thomson for the idea.
